data.description: Look no more! You'll LOVE this beautifully remodeled home, epitomizing comfortable living! Providing 3 beds, 2.5 baths, & a 2-car garage. Discover a welcoming open floor plan that fosters a sense of unity & ease! Natural light filled the spaces, complemented by two-tone paint and neutral & wood-look tile flooring downstairs. Cultivating kitchen perfect for family gatherings! Featuring black SS appliances, subway tile backsplash, a pantry, recessed lighting, white cabinetry w/crown molding, & a 2-tiered island w/breakfast bar. Flexible loft upstairs is ideal for a play area! The bedrooms, with plush carpet, ensure a restful night's sleep. Main bedroom has an ensuite w/dual sinks & a walk-in closet. Let's not forget the side yard, a great spot for enjoying BBQ! SELLER IS MOTIVATED. Act now!
